                 PART B - PARLIAMENTARY CONSTITUENCIES


   Sl. No. & Name                 Extent of Parliamentary Constituencies


1. North Goa              1-Mandrem; 2-Pernem (SC); 3-Bicholim; 4-Tivim; 5-Mapusa;
                          6-Siolim; 7-Saligao; 8-Calangute; 9-Porvorim; 10-Aldona;
                          11-Panaji; 12-Taleigao; 13-St. Cruz;         14-St. Andre;
                          15-Cumbarjua; 16-Mayem; 17-Sanquelim; 18-Poriem;
                          19-Valpoi and 20-Priol.

2. South Goa              21-Ponda;    22-Shiroda;   23-Marcaim   24-Mormugao;
                          25-Vasco-Da-Gama; 26-Dabolim 27-Cortalim; 28-Nuvem;
                          29-Curtorim; 30-Fatorda;     31-Margao; 32-Benaulim;
                          33-Navelim; 34-Cuncolim;       35-Velim; 36-Quepem;
                          37-Curchorem;        38-Sanvordem; 39-Sanguem and
                          40-Canacona.




NOTE :-    Any reference in Table A to a district, taluka, saza, village, Census Town
           (CT), Municipal Council(MCL), Out Growth(OG), ward or other territorial
           division shall be taken to mean the area comprised within that district,
           taluka, saza, village, Census Town(CT), Municipal Council(MCL), Out
           Growth(OG),and ward or other territorial division as on the 23rd day of
           March, 2005.




                                         114
